    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are hotlines, but it doesnt change the fact that i'm just... empty. it's not even sadness anymore, it's just nothingness. like the pilot has left the plane and it's just drifting. what's the point of even maintaining the vessel if there's no one left inside to experience it?",
